channel.title: Warm Springs Highway on Roadsign Pictures
channel.description: Recent content in Warm Springs Highway on Roadsign Pictures

item.title: US-26 West at OR-35 North
item.description: US-26 West at OR-35 North. Use OR-35 North for Hood River; US-26 West for Portland. Mount Hood is in the background of the photograph.

item.title: US-26 West Approaching OR-35
item.description: US-26 West approaching OR-35 in Clackamas County. Use OR-35 north for Mount Hood Meadows Ski Area; US-26 West for Government Camp.

item.title: US-26 West - Mount Hood Meadows
item.description: US-26 west approaching OR-35 North. Use OR-35 north for Mount Hood Meadows Ski Area.

item.title: US-26 West Approaching OR-35
item.description: US-26 West approaching OR-35 North to Hood River.

item.title: US-26 West - Clackamas County / Wapinita Pass
item.description: US-26 West at Clackamas County and Wapinita Pass - Elevation 3952 Feet. Wapinita Pass is at the crest of the Cascade Range.

item.title: US-26 West - Blue Box Summit
item.description: US-26 West at Blue Box Summit - Elevation 4024 Feet.

item.title: US-26 West - Timothy Lake/Olallie Lake Jct.
item.description: US-26 West approaching Timothy Lake/Olallie Lake Jct. (FS Road 42 - Skyline Road). Use FS Road 42 for access to the Clackamas River.

item.title: US-26 West at OR-216
item.description: US-26 West at OR-216 west to Maupin.

item.title: US-26 West - Wasco County
item.description: Entering Wasco County on US-26 west. Mount Hood is in the background.

item.title: US-26 West - South Warm Springs
item.description: South Warm Springs junction on US-26 west.

item.title: US-26 West - Warm Springs Veterans Mem. Highway
item.description: US-26 West - Warm Springs Veterans Memorial Highway. US-26 is designated the Warm Springs Veterans Memorial Highway through the Warm Springs Indian Reservation.

item.title: US-26 West - Deschutes River
item.description: Crossing the Deschutes River on US-26 West - Jefferson County.

item.title: US-97 North/US-26 West at US-26/US-97 Split
item.description: US-97 North/US-26 West at US-26/US-97 Split. Turn right to continue north on US-97.

item.title: US-97 North/US-26 West Approaching US-97/US-26 Split
item.description: US-97 North/US-26 West Approaching US-97/US-26 split in Madras. Turn right for US-97 North to Biggs and The Dalles. Continue straight for US-26 West to Mount Hood and Portland.

item.title: US-97 South at US-26
item.description: US-97 south at US-26. Turn right for US-26 west to Portland. Turn left for US-26 east and US-97 south to Redmond, Prineville, and Bend. US-26 joins US-97 south through Madras.

item.title: US-97 South Approaching US-26
item.description: US-97 south approaching US-26 in Madras.
